S.FORM: Singapore hya' ga cyux maki' tay 1 22 N, 103 48 E na Aziya' syuw. kwara' kinghciyan niya' 697 sq km (maki' tay 192ginkgan kin wahci') (kinwhci' niya' ga 687 sq km , kinwhci' na lawsayan wsilung hya' ga 10 sq km) Kinkhmayan kwara' squliq hya' ga 5,781,728. Pinbcyan naha' sni' naha' rhzyal hya' iy pqmahun hya' ga 1% , lhlahuy hya' ga 3.30%, sni' naha' sa pptzyuwaw sa bzinah hya' ga 95.70%. spzyang qalang na Kokka' spzyang naha' krahu' qalang hya' ga Singapore. snyan kinramat inlungan na Kokka' snyan kinramat inlungan na Kokka' hya' ga 9 na tay mspat byacing na qutux kawas. mrhuw Kokka' mrhuw Kokka' ta' misuw hya' ga Tony Tan, aring ryax 1 squ byacing tay 9 sa kawas 2011 lga, musa' spazyang balay ms'rux kya la. cinkhulan sa knita' sa brbiru' CIA 外交部
